# Disk usage (du): Defaults to show the size of every file in every folder, infinitely deep, in bytes.

# Shows summary of everything, in human-readable format:
du -sh

# Shows summary of everything, listed by folder, in human-readable format:
du -d 1 -hc

# To sort folder/files by size, in MB (-B MB), one folder deep (-d 1):
du -c -d 1 -B MB | sort -rn
